title: Hour 1 - Lefty Speaks, Deshaun Delays
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Lefty Speaks, Deshaun Delays
description:
Dan addresses Phil Mickelson's comments (or lack thereof) about the PGA Tour. And he expresses doubts about Browns QB Deshaun Watson being eligible to play in week 1 of the NFL season.
